  "description": "<p>Another day wasted! <br /><br />Lying low at home/ nesting around after graduating/ORD/just left your old job!</p><p>Remember your ambitions and goals to get into a great company or start yourself in an amazing company filled with opportunities.<br /><br /><strong>Your Role</strong></p><ul><li>Connect with new clients & manage their journey.</li></ul><ul><li>Build relationships through face-to-face engagement.</li></ul><ul><li>Present ideas, support campaigns & events.</li></ul><ul><li>Motivate and be a support to your team.<br /></li></ul><p><strong>What we offer</strong></p><ul><li>Regional & international exposure</li></ul><ul><li>Mentorship & career growth</li></ul><ul><li>Rewards & recognition</li></ul><ul><li>Leadership development<br /></li></ul><p><strong>Looking for</strong></p><ul><li>Energetic individuals with amazing vibes</li><li>Able to talk to strangers</li><li>Like a company that values your performances</li><li>Learners! That’s always prioritising to learn</li><li>You like to travel everywhere in Singapore and also internationally</li><li>0 experience in sales/marketing/customer-facing jobs</li><li>You are a super team player</li></ul><p>Step into a high-growth career with a dynamic team!</p>",
